keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map ; LinkHints.activateMode
map h previousTab
map l nextTab
map gu goToRoot
map gU goUp
map d scrollPageDown
map u scrollPageUp
map D scrollFullPageDown
map U scrollFullPageUp
map X restoreTab
map <c-X> removeTab
map M toggleMuteTab

unmap p
unmap x
unmap ^
unmap [[
